ss Seine-Saint-Denis.\", \"from\": 2251, \"to\": 2324, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his optimism\", \"from\": 2260, \"to\": 2272}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 2290, \"to\": 2298}, {\"ngram\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 2306, \"to\": 2323}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There are two extremes,\\\" said Cecile Gintrac of Vigilance JO, a local watchdog group.\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2412, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2364, \"end\": 2371, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gintrac\", \"score\": 0.8020135056820301, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gintrac\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gintrac\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gintrac\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"two extremes\", \"from\": 2337, \"to\": 2349}, {\"ngram\": \"Vigilance JO\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2387}, {\"ngram\": \"a local watchdog group\", \"from\": 2389, \"to\": 2411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One part of Paris is going to be a big party, while the other will not be able to go to work or get around because of all the Olympic road closures and restrictions.\\\"\", \"from\": 2414, \"to\": 2581, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2427, \"end\": 2432, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1479529955593348e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One part\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2423}, {\"ngram\": \"a big party\", \"from\": 2448, \"to\": 2459}, {\"ngram\": \"all the Olympic road closures\", \"from\": 2533, \"to\": 2562}, {\"ngram\": \"restrictions\", \"from\": 2567, \"to\": 2579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Delivery driver Moussa Syla, who lives in the Francs-Moisins estate - which is also getting a major facelift - said of the anticipated disruption: \\\"It is going to be a nightmare to get around.\\\"\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Delivery driver Moussa Syla\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2610}, {\"ngram\": \"the Francs-Moisins estate\", \"from\": 2625, \"to\": 2650}, {\"ngram\": \"a major facelift\", \"from\": 2675, \"to\": 2691}, {\"ngram\": \"the anticipated disruption\", \"from\": 2702, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"a nightmare\", \"from\": 2749, \"to\": 2760}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is hard to go anywhere in Seine-Saint-Denis these days without seeing scaffolding or cranes building whole new neighbourhoods.\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2907, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"from\": 2807, \"to\": 2824}, {\"ngram\": \"scaffolding\", \"from\": 2851, \"to\": 2862}, {\"ngram\": \"cranes\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2872}, {\"ngram\": \"whole new neighbourhoods\", \"from\": 2882, \"to\": 2906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Olympics are part of a long-term push to drag up the department that began with the symbolic decision to build the Stade de France there for the 1998 World Cup.\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 3073, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Olympics\", \"from\": 2909, \"to\": 2921}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 2926, \"to\": 2930}, {\"ngram\": \"a long-term push\", \"from\": 2934, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 2962, \"to\": 2976}, {\"ngram\": \"the symbolic decision\", \"from\": 2993, \"to\": 3014}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 3024, \"to\": 3043}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1998 World Cup\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3072}]}, {\"sentence\": \"High property prices in Paris and a massive soon-to-deliveredextension of its metro system into Seine-Saint-Denishas made the area attractive for developers.\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3099, \"end\": 3104, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1479529955593348e-24, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"High property prices\", \"from\": 3075, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive soon-to-deliveredextension\", \"from\": 3109, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"its metro system\", \"from\": 3149, \"to\": 3165}, {\"ngram\": \"Seine-Saint-Denishas\", \"from\": 3171, \"to\": 3191}, {\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 3197, \"to\": 3205}, {\"ngram\": \"developers\", \"from\": 3221, \"to\": 3231}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We need to find a second wind for Seine-Saint-Denis so jobs stay here,\\\" said Isabelle Vallentin of Solideo, the state body charged with delivering the Olympic projects.\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3403, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3269, \"end\": 3286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}, {\"begin\": 3312, \"end\": 3320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feral_child\", \"score\": 0.9999996068291557, \"rank\": 2.735582332393114e-07, \"text\": \"Isabelle\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feral_child\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Feral_child\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a second wind\", \"from\": 3251, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 3290, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"Solideo\", \"from\": 3334, \"to\": 3341}, {\"ngram\": \"the state body\", \"from\": 3343, \"to\": 3357}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic projects\", \"from\": 3382, \"to\": 3402}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And Seine-Saint-Denis' \\\"extremely decrepit housing has to be developed\\\", she added.\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3488, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3409, \"end\": 3426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"A large slice of the \\u20ac4.5 billion (S$6.6 billion) building budget for the Games is going into this push, with the department the big winner, taking around 80 per cent of \\u20ac1.7 billion in public money.\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3689, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A large slice\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3503}, {\"ngram\": \"building budget\", \"from\": 3540, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3560, \"to\": 3569}, {\"ngram\": \"this push\", \"from\": 3584, \"to\": 3593}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 3600, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"80 per cent\", \"from\": 3645, \"to\": 3656}, {\"ngram\": \"public money\", \"from\": 3676, \"to\": 3688}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athletes' village, the Games' biggest building project and a whole new eco-neighbourhood in itself, will house 14,500 athletes and their support teams as well as 9,000 Paralympians and their staff.\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3892, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athletes' village\", \"from\": 3691, \"to\": 3712}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games' biggest building project\", \"from\": 3714, \"to\": 3749}, {\"ngram\": \"a whole new eco-neighbourhood\", \"from\": 3754, \"to\": 3783}, {\"ngram\": \"14,500 athletes\", \"from\": 3806, \"to\": 3821}, {\"ngram\": \"their support teams\", \"from\": 3826, \"to\": 3845}, {\"ngram\": \"9,000 Paralympians\", \"from\": 3857, \"to\": 3875}, {\"ngram\": \"their staff\", \"from\": 3880, \"to\": 3891}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once the Paralympics end, the village will morph into a mixed neighbourhood of apartments and offices, the first of its 6,000 new residents moving in early in 2025, followed by a similar number of workers.\", \"from\": 3894, \"to\": 4099, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paralympics end\", \"from\": 3899, \"to\": 3918}, {\"ngram\": \"the village\", \"from\": 3920, \"to\": 3931}, {\"ngram\": \"a mixed neighbourhood\", \"from\": 3948, \"to\": 3969}, {\"ngram\": \"apartments\", \"from\": 3973, \"to\": 3983}, {\"ngram\": \"offices\", \"from\": 3988, \"to\": 3995}, {\"ngram\": \"its 6,000 new residents\", \"from\": 4010, \"to\": 4033}, {\"ngram\": \"a similar number\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4087}, {\"ngram\": \"workers\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But only a third of the 2,800 apartments will be sold on the open market.\", \"from\": 4101, \"to\": 4174, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only a third\", \"from\": 4105, \"to\": 4117}, {\"ngram\": \"the 2,800 apartments\", \"from\": 4121, \"to\": 4141}, {\"ngram\": \"the open market\", \"from\": 4158, \"to\": 4173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Contrary to previous Games like London - where the organisers were accused of \\\"gentrification on an industrial scale\\\" and not keeping their promises to locals - Solideo's Vallentin said they insisted developers \\\"respond first to (local) housing needs\\\".\", \"from\": 4176, \"to\": 4429, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4208, \"end\": 4214, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"score\": 0.9999999174615403, \"rank\": 8.171822631477684e-08, \"text\": \"London\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/London\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"previous Games\", \"from\": 4188, \"to\": 4202}, {\"ngram\": \"the organisers\", \"from\": 4223, \"to\": 4237}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"gentrification\", \"from\": 4254, \"to\": 4269}, {\"ngram\": \"an industrial scale\", \"from\": 4273, \"to\": 4292}, {\"ngram\": \"their promises\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4324}, {\"ngram\": \"locals - Solideo's Vallentin\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4356}, {\"ngram\": \"developers\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4386}, {\"ngram\": \"(local) housing needs\", \"from\": 4405, \"to\": 4426}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So 25 to 40 per cent of the apartments will go to social housing, with the rest let out at \\\"affordable\\\" rents through semi-public housing bodies.\", \"from\": 4431, \"to\": 4576, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"25 to 40 per cent\", \"from\": 4434, \"to\": 4451}, {\"ngram\": \"the apartments\", \"from\": 4455, \"to\": 4469}, {\"ngram\": \"social housing\", \"from\": 4481, \"to\": 4495}, {\"ngram\": \"the rest\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4510}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"affordable\\\" rents\", \"from\": 4522, \"to\": 4540}, {\"ngram\": \"semi-public housing bodies\", \"from\": 4549, \"to\": 4575}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis' other big-headline win is a clutch of new swimming pools, of which it is in dire need.\", \"from\": 4578, \"to\": 4683, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4578, \"end\": 4595, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a clutch\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4631}, {\"ngram\": \"new swimming pools\", \"from\": 4635, \"to\": 4653}, {\"ngram\": \"dire need\", \"from\": 4673, \"to\": 4682}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The most eye-catching is the Olympic Aquatic Centre, built opposite the Stade de France where the diving, water polo and artistic swimming medals will be decided.\", \"from\": 4685, \"to\": 4847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4714, \"end\": 4736, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens_Olympic_Sports_Complex\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.171837449064218e-14, \"text\": \"Olympic Aquatic Centre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens_Olympic_Sports_Complex\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Athens_Olympic_Sports_Complex\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 4753, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"the diving\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4789}, {\"ngram\": \"water polo\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4801}, {\"ngram\": \"artistic swimming medals\", \"from\": 4806, \"to\": 4830}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It will also get the main Olympic pool, which is to be dismantled and divided in two after the Games, as well as a new training pool.\", \"from\": 4849, \"to\": 4982, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the main Olympic pool\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4887}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 4940, \"to\": 4949}, {\"ngram\": \"a new training pool\", \"from\": 4962, \"to\": 4981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Olympic-related sites have been popping up like confetti across Seine-Saint-Denis, with the little town of Dugny likely to be transformed by the Games.\", \"from\": 4984, \"to\": 5135, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5048, \"end\": 5065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}, {\"begin\": 5091, \"end\": 5096, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dugny\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Olympic-related sites\", \"from\": 4984, \"to\": 5005}, {\"ngram\": \"the little town\", \"from\": 5072, \"to\": 5087}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5125, \"to\": 5134}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Its population is set to grow by a third with housing on a site inherited from the Olympics' \\\"media cluster\\\".\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5246, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Its population\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5151}, {\"ngram\": \"a third\", \"from\": 5170, \"to\": 5177}, {\"ngram\": \"housing\", \"from\": 5183, \"to\": 5190}, {\"ngram\": \"a site\", \"from\": 5194, \"to\": 5200}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics' \\\"media cluster\", \"from\": 5216, \"to\": 5244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Badly served by public transport until now, Dugny is using the Games to diversify its housing stock, 77 per cent of which is social housing - the highest rate in France.\", \"from\": 5247, \"to\": 5416, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5291, \"end\": 5296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dugny\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\"}, {\"begin\": 5409, \"end\": 5415, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999999999809006, \"rank\": 1.927457786093397e-11, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"public transport\", \"from\": 5263, \"to\": 5279}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 5306, \"to\": 5315}, {\"ngram\": \"its housing stock\", \"from\": 5329, \"to\": 5346}, {\"ngram\": \"77 per cent\", \"from\": 5348, \"to\": 5359}, {\"ngram\": \"social housing\", \"from\": 5372, \"to\": 5386}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest rate\", \"from\": 5389, \"to\": 5405}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One-third of the 1,400 new homes are being set aside to help get people on the property ladder.\", \"from\": 5418, \"to\": 5513, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"third\", \"from\": 5422, \"to\": 5427}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1,400 new homes\", \"from\": 5431, \"to\": 5450}, {\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 5483, \"to\": 5489}, {\"ngram\": \"the property ladder\", \"from\": 5493, \"to\": 5512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dugny's mayor Quentin Gesell said many of his friends \\\"who had grown up like me in Dugny have had to leave because they can neither buy here nor rent (their incomes being too high for social housing) when they would have preferred to stay close to their families\\\".\", \"from\": 5515, \"to\": 5779, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5515, \"end\": 5520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dugny\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\"}, {\"begin\": 5598, \"end\": 5603, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dugny\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dugny\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Quentin Gesell\", \"from\": 5529, \"to\": 5543}, {\"ngram\": \"his friends\", \"from\": 5557, \"to\": 5568}, {\"ngram\": \"their incomes\", \"from\": 5666, \"to\": 5679}, {\"ngram\": \"social housing\", \"from\": 5699, \"to\": 5713}, {\"ngram\": \"their families\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 5777}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Another more subtle transformation is likely to come through a series of new footbridges linking areas long divided by the major road and rail arteries that slice through the department.\", \"from\": 5781, \"to\": 5967, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Another more subtle transformation\", \"from\": 5781, \"to\": 5815}, {\"ngram\": \"a series\", \"from\": 5842, \"to\": 5850}, {\"ngram\": \"new footbridges\", \"from\": 5854, \"to\": 5869}, {\"ngram\": \"areas\", \"from\": 5878, \"to\": 5883}, {\"ngram\": \"the major road and rail arteries\", \"from\": 5900, \"to\": 5932}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 5952, \"to\": 5966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back near the Francs-Moisins estate, a foot and bike bridge is being built across the Saint-Denis canal to the Stade de France, replacing an old and unreliable rotating road bridge and a steep-stepped pedestrian crossing.\", \"from\": 5969, \"to\": 6190, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Francs-Moisins estate\", \"from\": 5979, \"to\": 6004}, {\"ngram\": \"a foot and bike bridge\", \"from\": 6006, \"to\": 6028}, {\"ngram\": \"the Saint-Denis canal\", \"from\": 6051, \"to\": 6072}, {\"ngram\": \"the Stade de France\", \"from\": 6076, \"to\": 6095}, {\"ngram\": \"an old and unreliable rotating road bridge\", \"from\": 6107, \"to\": 6149}, {\"ngram\": \"a steep-stepped pedestrian crossing\", \"from\": 6154, \"to\": 6189}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's a nightmare to cross now,\\\" said Karene, a mother of three.\", \"from\": 6192, \"to\": 6256, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a nightmare\", \"from\": 6198, \"to\": 6209}, {\"ngram\": \"Karene\", \"from\": 6230, \"to\": 6236}, {\"ngram\": \"a mother\", \"from\": 6238, \"to\": 6246}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"You have to fold up the pram and take the baby in the other arm.\", \"from\": 6258, \"to\": 6323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the pram\", \"from\": 6279, \"to\": 6287}, {\"ngram\": \"the baby\", \"from\": 6297, \"to\": 6305}, {\"ngram\": \"the other arm\", \"from\": 6309, \"to\": 6322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So this is really great, a real plus for the area.\\\"\", \"from\": 6324, \"to\": 6375, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the area\", \"from\": 6365, \"to\": 6373}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bridge had been talked of for years but the Games finally got it over the line.\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6460, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bridge\", \"from\": 6377, \"to\": 6387}, {\"ngram\": \"years\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6416}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6421, \"to\": 6430}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 6451, \"to\": 6459}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Stephane Troussel, the socialist head of Seine-Saint-Denis council, said that the Olympics have been the \\\"pivot point that has accelerated the transformation\\\" of the department.\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6639, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6503, \"end\": 6520, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Stephane Troussel\", \"from\": 6462, \"to\": 6479}, {\"ngram\": \"the socialist head\", \"from\": 6481, \"to\": 6499}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 6540, \"to\": 6552}, {\"ngram\": \"the \\\"pivot point\", \"from\": 6563, \"to\": 6579}, {\"ngram\": \"the transformation\", \"from\": 6601, \"to\": 6619}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 6624, \"to\": 6638}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In record time we have managed to deliver a huge amount of infrastructure, housing, roads and bridges,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 6641, \"to\": 6754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"record time\", \"from\": 6645, \"to\": 6656}, {\"ngram\": \"a huge amount\", \"from\": 6684, \"to\": 6697}, {\"ngram\": \"infrastructure\", \"from\": 6701, \"to\": 6715}, {\"ngram\": \"housing\", \"from\": 6717, \"to\": 6724}, {\"ngram\": \"roads\", \"from\": 6726, \"to\": 6731}, {\"ngram\": \"bridges\", \"from\": 6736, \"to\": 6743}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there are doubts over the jobs the Games promised to deliver to the department, whose 10.4 per cent unemployment rate is nearly a third higher than the national average.\", \"from\": 6756, \"to\": 6929, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doubts\", \"from\": 6770, \"to\": 6776}, {\"ngram\": \"the jobs\", \"from\": 6782, \"to\": 6790}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6791, \"to\": 6800}, {\"ngram\": \"the department\", \"from\": 6824, \"to\": 6838}, {\"ngram\": \"whose 10.4 per cent unemployment rate\", \"from\": 6840, \"to\": 6877}, {\"ngram\": \"the national average\", \"from\": 6908, \"to\": 6928}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While around 180,000 people will work at the Games, according to official estimates, most will be on short-term contracts, such as the 6,000 people taken on by Sodexo for catering at the athletes' village.\", \"from\": 6931, \"to\": 7136, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7091, \"end\": 7097, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sodexo\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sodexo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around 180,000 people\", \"from\": 6937, \"to\": 6958}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 6972, \"to\": 6981}, {\"ngram\": \"official estimates\", \"from\": 6996, \"to\": 7014}, {\"ngram\": \"short-term contracts\", \"from\": 7032, \"to\": 7052}, {\"ngram\": \"the 6,000 people\", \"from\": 7062, \"to\": 7078}, {\"ngram\": \"the athletes' village\", \"from\": 7114, \"to\": 7135}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Beyond that, though, one of the biggest Olympics legacies could be how Seine-Saint-Denis is seen.\", \"from\": 7138, \"to\": 7235, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7209, \"end\": 7226, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the biggest Olympics legacies\", \"from\": 7166, \"to\": 7195}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police have already stepped up operations targeting drug dealers and a massive security operation is planned for the Games.\", \"from\": 7237, \"to\": 7360, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Police\", \"from\": 7237, \"to\": 7243}, {\"ngram\": \"operations\", \"from\": 7268, \"to\": 7278}, {\"ngram\": \"drug dealers\", \"from\": 7289, \"to\": 7301}, {\"ngram\": \"a massive security operation\", \"from\": 7306, \"to\": 7334}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 7350, \"to\": 7359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In welcoming visitors from all over the world this summer, Seine-Saint-Denis hopes to write a new chapter in its history, one that plays up its diversity and potential rather than crime and sporadic outbursts of rioting.\", \"from\": 7362, \"to\": 7582, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7421, \"end\": 7438, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"visitors\", \"from\": 7375, \"to\": 7383}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 7398, \"to\": 7407}, {\"ngram\": \"a new chapter\", \"from\": 7454, \"to\": 7467}, {\"ngram\": \"its history\", \"from\": 7471, \"to\": 7482}, {\"ngram\": \"its diversity\", \"from\": 7502, \"to\": 7515}, {\"ngram\": \"potential\", \"from\": 7520, \"to\": 7529}, {\"ngram\": \"crime\", \"from\": 7542, \"to\": 7547}, {\"ngram\": \"sporadic outbursts\", \"from\": 7552, \"to\": 7570}, {\"ngram\": \"rioting\", \"from\": 7574, \"to\": 7581}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Back on the Francs-Moisins estate, Karene is praying that \\\"the visibility\\\" will do everyone good.\", \"from\": 7584, \"to\": 7681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Francs-Moisins estate\", \"from\": 7592, \"to\": 7617}, {\"ngram\": \"Karene\", \"from\": 7619, \"to\": 7625}, {\"ngram\": \"the visibility\", \"from\": 7643, \"to\": 7657}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 7667, \"to\": 7675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hope it is well organised, because if it is like the football (the chaotic scenes before the 2022 Champions League final), Saint-Denis' image will plummet again.\", \"from\": 7683, \"to\": 7847, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7784, \"end\": 7800, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.679206138865361e-38, \"text\": \"Champions League\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/UEFA_Champions_League\"}, {\"begin\": 7809, \"end\": 7820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"score\": 0.9999589184625113, \"rank\": 4.103646029527813e-05, \"text\": \"Saint-Denis\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine-Saint-Denis\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the football\", \"from\": 7735, \"to\": 7747}, {\"ngram\": \"the chaotic scenes\", \"from\": 7749, \"to\": 7767}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"AFP Olympics Olympics 2024 France E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms & Conditions Personal Data Protection Notice Need help?\", \"from\": 7847, \"to\": 8003, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"AFP Olympics Olympics 2024 France E-paper Newsletters Podcasts RSS Feed About Us Terms\", \"from\": 7848, \"to\": 7934}, {\"ngram\": \"Conditions\", \"from\": 7937, \"to\": 7947}, {\"ngram\": \"Personal Data Protection Notice\", \"from\": 7948, \"to\": 7979}, {\"ngram\": \"help\", \"from\": 7985, \"to\": 7989}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Reach us here.\", \"from\": 8004, \"to\": 8018, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8010, \"to\": 8012}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertise with us\", \"from\": 8020, \"to\": 8037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Advertise\", \"from\": 8020, \"to\": 8029}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 8035, \"to\": 8037}]}]}"